    • HITBOX

      static final EntityDataType<CompoundTag> HITBOX
      Set custom hitboxes for an entity. This will override the hitbox defined with SCALE, WIDTH and HEIGHT, but will not affect the collisions. Setting the hitbox to an empty list will revert to default behaviour.

      NBT format 

       {
     "Hitboxes": [
          {
              "MinX": 0f,
              "MinY": 0f,
              "MinZ": 0f,
              "MaxX": 1f,
              "MaxY": 1f,
              "MaxZ": 1f,
              "PivotX": 0f,
              "PivotY": 0f,
              "PivotZ": 0f,
          }
     ]
 }
